channel.title: Need a little help with portforwarding :S
channel.description:
Hello, yes I know there is a whole tut on this very subject, But the thing is i have my server running (I can connect to it from a local port "127.0.0.1") and, I am the only person that can connect, I went into my router and maid the port 43594-43594 however, I do not understand why no one else can connect. My router brand is "Intellinet, Active networking", If anyone could support me with this Mishap I would appriciate it.
Thank you, ~Sincerly~ Microsoft1.
